00:21:42,630 --> 00:21:46,559
Is she a reader of penny romances, and fond of the theatre?

00:21:46,559 --> 00:21:52,160
her? Alice is a good girl, sir, though she loves the gallery, and will sometimes quote lines as

00:21:52,160 --> 00:21:58,099
