00:22:20,090 --> 00:22:22,530
But I beg you not to frighten her more than is needed.

00:22:22,530 --> 00:22:26,710
Alice, a slim, pretty creature with anxious eyes, entered at a curtsy.

00:22:26,710 --> 00:22:34,759
And Holmes addressed her with that austere kindness which makes the simple tell the truth as if they had always meant to do so and had only been waiting for permission.

00:22:34,759 --> 00:22:35,839
..

00:22:35,839 --> 00:22:42,400
Alice, the truth is the cheapest ribbon you can buy and the strongest, did you, in the last week?

00:22:42,400 --> 00:22:45,920
....

00:22:45,920 --> 00:22:49,140
