00:23:04,059 --> 00:23:07,900
She was kind to me and spoke as though she were my sister.

00:23:07,900 --> 00:23:08,579
Mr. Huh!

00:23:08,579 --> 00:23:10,940
...

00:23:10,940 --> 00:23:11,440
Yay!

00:23:11,440 --> 00:23:12,900
..

00:23:12,900 --> 00:23:15,039
And she asked me how one might get a footman

00:23:15,039 --> 00:23:16,839
to look the other way at a ball

00:23:16,839 --> 00:23:19,679
if the footman were honest but human.

00:23:19,679 --> 00:23:21,929
And did she tell you her name?

00:23:21,929 --> 00:23:24,420
