00:23:24,420 --> 00:23:26,940
besides the pleasure of friendly talk?

00:23:26,940 --> 00:23:29,059
Miss Sybil Hart, sir,

00:23:29,059 --> 00:23:31,180
as she gave me a little book of verses

00:23:31,180 --> 00:23:33,759
