00:23:35,250 --> 00:23:37,700
Oh, I never do.

00:23:37,700 --> 00:23:39,269
I never do.

00:23:39,269 --> 00:23:42,460
Holmes inclined his head, satisfied, satisfied.

00:23:42,460 --> 00:23:47,140
And when the girl had withdrawn, he turned to us with that peculiar brightness in his gaze

00:23:47,140 --> 00:23:49,210
which signals the construction of a plan.

00:23:49,210 --> 00:23:54,279
As if the mind had just hung a new chandelier and was testing the switches with a finger of light.

00:23:54,279 --> 00:23:55,440
..

00:23:55,440 --> 00:23:58,530
The plot thickens with Flower and Lise Watson.

00:23:58,530 --> 00:24:02,160
We have a colonel with a fox's head cane.

00:24:02,160 --> 00:24:08,059
a journalist with a black ribbon, a stage prince with admirers and missing confetti,

00:24:08,059 --> 00:24:11,509
and a cipher that goes from river stair to looking glass.

00:24:11,509 --> 00:24:17,230
Tonight, at midnight, we shall keep the appointment, though not as commanded,

00:24:17,230 --> 00:24:21,500
and we shall see whether the slipper breaks or the spell does.

00:24:21,500 --> 00:24:26,789
It was agreed that I should act as decoy, for I bore no resemblance to a lady in white,

00:24:26,789 --> 00:24:29,880
and it is exactly in that absence that a trap can be baited,

00:24:29,880 --> 00:24:33,440
if a man be cautious and a friend be near with a cord and a pair of cuffs,

00:24:33,440 --> 00:24:35,099
we return to Baker Street to prepare.

00:24:35,099 --> 00:24:37,319
And there I watched Holmes arrange our little stage

00:24:37,319 --> 00:24:40,430
with the cool zest of a manager mounting a new piece.

00:24:40,430 --> 00:24:44,500
You shall stand upon the stair where the triangles meet,

00:24:44,500 --> 00:24:47,069
Watson, with the casket empty,

00:24:47,069 --> 00:24:49,909
but so ballasted as to persuade,

00:24:49,909 --> 00:24:52,920
I shall keep the shadow to your north,

00:24:52,920 --> 00:24:56,619
and we shall allow the watcher to reveal himself

00:24:56,619 --> 00:25:02,839
yourself by the angle of his impatience. Do not be heroic, be punctual.

00:25:02,839 --> 00:25:04,099
..

00:25:04,099 --> 00:25:09,059
Poor Admidnight found us in position. The river lapped and the stone breathed its damp for long

00:25:09,059 --> 00:25:14,099
minutes. No, thing occurred, but the swell of the tide and the far-off walls of some late house

00:25:14,099 --> 00:25:19,980
where the party ha, dee, long outstayed propriety. Then there came a rustle as of silk, denied a

00:25:19,980 --> 00:25:25,660
stage, and a figure in a pale cloak, slim and must, stood at the top of the stair like a thought that

00:25:25,660 --> 00:25:26,720
