00:25:41,809 --> 00:25:43,700
Miss Sybil Hart,

00:25:43,700 --> 00:25:45,740
you could not hold your tongue

00:25:45,740 --> 00:25:47,829
even if the plot depended upon it.

00:25:47,829 --> 00:25:50,160
Tell us quickly how you come to Bali

00:25:50,160 --> 00:25:52,079
on the wrong side of the proscenium,

00:25:52,079 --> 00:25:54,359
and why I should not summon Lestrade

00:25:54,359 --> 00:25:58,329
to grant your column a freshness it seldom enjoys.

00:25:58,329 --> 00:26:00,980
Hmm, because, sir, hmm,

00:26:00,980 --> 00:26:03,240
the prince you hunt threatens ladies

00:26:03,240 --> 00:26:04,949
who will never forgive the police,

00:26:04,949 --> 00:26:06,389
but might forgive a pen.

00:26:06,389 --> 00:26:09,359
And because I have traced him to a ring of gentlemen

00:26:09,359 --> 00:26:11,920
who gamble away fortunes they do not own

00:26:11,920 --> 00:26:14,429
and recover them by charming pledges out of innocence,

00:26:14,429 --> 00:26:17,769
let me help you, and I will earn, for once,

00:26:17,769 --> 00:26:19,529
a headline that is honest.

00:26:19,529 --> 00:26:22,819
Her voice carried an edge of fearless mockery

00:26:22,819 --> 00:26:26,619
and yet a gravity that made mockery seem a form of coup.

00:26:26,619 --> 00:26:27,720
Oh!

00:26:27,720 --> 00:26:29,110
Rage, Holmes.

00:26:29,110 --> 00:26:32,559
Coup prizes evidence but also admires style

00:26:32,559 --> 00:26:34,159
where it supports truth.

00:26:34,159 --> 00:26:36,200
Lowered the hand that had gripped the cord

00:26:36,200 --> 00:26:37,759
and inclined his head a fraction.

00:26:37,759 --> 00:26:39,160
..

00:26:39,160 --> 00:26:40,180
Speak.

00:26:40,180 --> 00:26:42,680
Then, and be advised

00:26:42,680 --> 00:26:45,740
that the river is stingy with second chances.

00:26:45,740 --> 00:26:48,529
Name your prince and his throne.

00:26:48,529 --> 00:26:52,299
His nom de bal is Prince Charming, his true name.

00:26:52,299 --> 00:26:55,860
so far as any man with three club memberships has.

00:26:55,860 --> 00:26:58,539
A true name is Sir Alistair Mordaunt.

00:26:58,539 --> 00:27:02,159
His quartermaster is a soldier who left his honour in Bombay.

00:27:02,159 --> 00:27:05,160
His theatre is the Savoy when the lights are up

00:27:05,160 --> 00:27:07,990
and Holland House when they are down tomorrow night.

00:27:07,990 --> 00:27:10,480
There is a masked charity fete

00:27:10,480 --> 00:27:14,279
where he intends to collect three pledges in a single minuet.

00:27:14,279 --> 00:27:16,099
And if you are not there,

00:27:16,099 --> 00:27:20,480
the season will wake to scandal harsh enough to make ballad sheets fat.

00:27:20,480 --> 00:27:25,509
A shadow moved at the waterline, a second watcher, and before I could call out,

00:27:25,509 --> 00:27:29,159
Holmes's whistle split the gloom and a shape leapt from a skiff.

00:27:29,159 --> 00:27:33,230
Then another, there was a brief scuffle of feet and oats like broken glass,

00:27:33,230 --> 00:27:38,230
and our unseen listeners fled along the bank with the cat-like stride of men trained to vanish.

00:27:38,230 --> 00:27:42,039
They are cautious enough to keep their names for the program tomorrow.

00:27:42,039 --> 00:27:44,010
Very well, Miss Hart.

00:27:44,010 --> 00:27:47,530
You have bought yourself a seat in the orchestra, Watson.

00:27:47,530 --> 00:27:49,460
Polish your boots and your eyes.

00:27:49,460 --> 00:27:57,599
We, too, shall go to the ball, and I think our Prince will find his slip a pinches when

00:27:57,599 --> 00:28:01,039
worn upon a foot that does not fit."

00:28:01,039 --> 00:28:06,440
Holland House, on the appointed evening, glowed like a conjured palace, and its gardens held

00:28:06,440 --> 00:28:10,670
those whispering lamps which make sin and charity indistinguishable at a distance.

00:28:10,670 --> 00:28:15,119
Holmes, who affected a plain footman's livery with such exactitude that I caught myself

00:28:15,119 --> 00:28:19,180
myself twice about to hand him my gloves, had arranged the passes for our entrance by

00:28:19,180 --> 00:28:23,880
means known only to himself and perhaps to one flustered clerk whom he had hypnotized

00:28:23,880 --> 00:28:26,300
with logic and tipped with half a sovereign.

00:28:26,300 --> 00:28:32,059
Remember Watson, that a mask is a confession printed upon satin.

00:28:32,059 --> 00:28:38,579
The honest man wears his own face uneasily, and the scoundrel wears a false one, as if

00:28:38,579 --> 00:28:40,170
it had grown upon him.

00:28:40,170 --> 00:28:42,099
Keep to the edges!

00:28:42,099 --> 00:28:43,680
Observe the hands.

00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:50,140
hands, always the hands, and when the couplet is recited about pumpkins turning to coaches,

00:28:50,140 --> 00:28:54,639
note who glances toward the terrace, for he is rehearsing the exit.

00:28:54,639 --> 00:28:59,480
I shall take the gallery reserved for the press and ladies of uncertain profession.

00:28:59,480 --> 00:29:01,390
Do not scowl.

00:29:01,390 --> 00:29:03,099
Hmm, doctor, hmm.

00:29:03,099 --> 00:29:07,150
It is a life's work to inhabit uncertainty with a straight back.

00:29:07,150 --> 00:29:08,759
Signal me by the handkerchief.

00:29:08,759 --> 00:29:14,860
If your prince appears, I have notebooks within my bodice and daring where other women carry smelling salts.

00:29:14,860 --> 00:29:22,190
The band struck up, and the great room turned like a slow, complicated machine wound by women's shoulders and men's ambitions.

00:29:22,190 --> 00:29:28,250
I felt acutely my plainness and was grateful for it, for it allowed me to watch without being watched.

00:29:28,250 --> 00:29:33,799
