00:33:44,549 --> 00:33:45,539
In the conservatory,

00:33:45,539 --> 00:33:48,279
the lantern sent pale islands of light onto the gravel

00:33:48,279 --> 00:33:49,529
and the colonel turned,

00:33:49,529 --> 00:33:51,480
cane leveled like a small lance.

00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:53,279
I do not wish to hurt you doctor

00:33:53,279 --> 00:33:56,349
for you have the air of a decent man.

00:33:56,349 --> 00:33:59,319
Stand aside and let my affair pass by

00:33:59,319 --> 00:34:01,839
and I will lay my mouth upon silence

00:34:01,839 --> 00:34:03,460
as upon a Bible.

00:34:03,460 --> 00:34:05,630
You have already kissed away your oath.

00:34:05,630 --> 00:34:06,679
I advise surrender,

00:34:06,679 --> 00:34:09,720
for the house is surrounded by decency-wearing boots,

00:34:09,720 --> 00:34:12,610
and even the flowers here would testify if called.

00:34:12,610 --> 00:34:14,340
Never argue with a cavalryman

00:34:14,340 --> 00:34:16,029
when he has space to charge.

00:34:16,029 --> 00:34:17,619
Clip the space, Watson.

00:34:17,619 --> 00:34:19,150
Close, close,

00:34:19,150 --> 00:34:22,199
and turn his lance into a walking stick.

00:34:22,199 --> 00:34:24,010
I obeyed with a rush.

00:34:24,010 --> 00:34:25,360
Closing the distance,

00:34:25,360 --> 00:34:27,820
the Colonel's cane thrust and blanced from my shoulder.

00:34:27,820 --> 00:34:29,119
I seized it.

00:34:29,119 --> 00:34:30,139
Begleppled.

00:34:30,139 --> 00:34:30,380
Hmm.

00:34:30,380 --> 00:34:35,649
And Holmes appeared behind him with the light step of a cat that has learned to tread among glass.

00:34:35,649 --> 00:34:39,980
In an instant, the Colonel's arms were pinned by the black cord from Holmes' pocket.

00:34:39,980 --> 00:34:44,400
His cane burst in two and from the hollow inside fell a coil of fine wire

00:34:44,400 --> 00:34:49,769
and a tiny bottle of chloroform such as a theatre doctor might carry for fainting ingenues.

00:34:49,769 --> 00:34:55,679
A practical fellow, our Colonel, his honour, like his cane, is hollow

00:34:55,679 --> 00:34:59,000
and hides tools for removing obstacles, Watson.

00:34:59,000 --> 00:35:06,360
Watson secure his wrists Miss Hart Miss Hart do not faint for he has more than enough smelling

00:35:06,360 --> 00:35:13,380
salts for us all and none of it safe I am better at printing crimes than at fainting away from them

00:35:13,380 --> 00:35:20,320
I shall go to the gate and bring in your Lestrade like a chorus when the stage needs it do not allow

00:35:20,320 --> 00:35:25,800
Now, Sir Alastair, to improvise, for his ad-libs run to cruelty, eh?

00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:26,960
..

00:35:26,960 --> 00:35:32,380
Cruelty, madam, is a word ladies use to name justice when it turns and sees them.

00:35:32,380 --> 00:35:34,840
I will answer for nothing. I have not signed.

00:35:34,840 --> 00:35:39,649
And if Mr. Holmes has brought handwriting experts to a ball,

00:35:39,649 --> 00:35:42,440
I shall almost admire him between indictments.

00:35:42,440 --> 00:35:45,750
I have brought something more decisive than experts.

00:35:45,750 --> 00:35:50,019
Your own vanity. This ledger bears your private.

00:35:50,019 --> 00:36:07,320
marks the same which dented the toe of a gift slipper with a needle so that you might know your handiwork in a crowd your needle speaks across crystal the way a signature does across vellum i fear you have

00:36:07,320 --> 00:36:12,079
If by fear, ere been too original by half.

00:36:12,079 --> 00:36:30,380
...................

00:36:30,380 --> 00:36:31,219
Evening, Mister.

00:36:31,219 --> 00:36:32,320
..

00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:36,519
Holmes, I see your theatre has found its villain with admirable punctuality.

00:36:36,519 --> 00:36:40,769
Sir Alastair Mordaunt, you would be so good as to accompany me quietly, Colonel.

00:36:40,769 --> 00:36:42,900
I am sorry to find you a prop in this show.

00:36:42,900 --> 00:36:45,220
London will hiss where it once applauded.

00:36:45,220 --> 00:36:47,260
Spare your sermon for a cheaper gallery.

00:36:47,260 --> 00:36:50,940
We shall see if your handcuffs fit better than your morolet.

00:36:50,940 --> 00:36:51,860
Peace.

00:36:51,860 --> 00:36:54,500
...

00:36:54,500 --> 00:36:56,569
They generally do, Colonel.

00:36:56,569 --> 00:36:58,840
Your fox may run no more.

00:36:58,840 --> 00:37:03,619
I have marked all your holes, and they are now attended by watchmen

00:37:03,619 --> 00:37:07,880
who collect no bribes and applaud no dramatics.

00:37:07,880 --> 00:37:09,400
..

00:37:09,400 --> 00:37:12,510
The allister kept his poise even as the steel embraced him.

00:37:12,510 --> 00:37:14,930
He looked at the room of the practice, licking to show it.

00:37:14,930 --> 00:37:17,930
Contempt of a man who has bought applause and knows its price.

00:37:17,930 --> 00:37:19,840
And yet, as he passed Miss Hart,

00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:23,099
I saw a flicker cross his eyes like the memory of some single kindness

00:37:23,099 --> 00:37:25,390
that had not been part of any plan.

00:37:25,390 --> 00:37:30,920
Take him, Inspector. Mr. Holmes has done the art and you must do the craft.

00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:35,250
And when London reads of it, I shall print as little of the ladies as the truth permits,

00:37:35,250 --> 00:37:39,000
for I am not in the business of breaking slippers in the street.

00:37:39,000 --> 00:37:45,500
Then, Miss Hart, you are in the business of mending them, which is a rarer trade.

00:37:45,500 --> 00:37:51,130
Come, Watson, we must see the Duchess, and return to her the liberty of her niece,

00:37:51,130 --> 00:37:53,390
and the education of her household.

00:37:53,390 --> 00:37:59,059
After that, perhaps, I shall permit myself an heir upon the violin in D,

00:37:59,059 --> 00:38:02,359
D, which is the key of restorative conclusions.

00:38:02,359 --> 00:38:05,159
The Duchess of Ravenscar received us in her library

00:38:05,159 --> 00:38:08,220
with a composure that only magnified the tremor.

00:38:08,220 --> 00:38:09,960
Of her hand upon the bell-pull,

00:38:09,960 --> 00:38:12,679
Lady Beatrice hovered near like a penitent angel

00:38:12,679 --> 00:38:15,519
while servants came and went like discreet punctuation.

00:38:15,519 --> 00:38:17,920
The house seemed to exhale relief in the way.

00:38:17,920 --> 00:38:20,300
Lambs do when their wicks are trimmed.

00:38:20,300 --> 00:38:21,699
..

00:38:21,699 --> 00:38:26,900
Mr. Holmes, I have had news enough to make an old woman of me

00:38:26,900 --> 00:38:29,090
and grace enough to keep me standing?

00:38:29,090 --> 00:38:30,409
Is it done?

00:38:30,409 --> 00:38:34,730
And can the child sleep without dreaming of masks and staircases?

00:38:34,730 --> 00:38:39,710
It is done, insofar as the principal actors have been bowed off,

00:38:39,710 --> 00:38:42,760
Sir Alistair Mordaunt and Colonel Moe.

00:38:42,760 --> 00:38:48,909
Redaunt, no relations except in enterprise are at Scotland Yard,

00:38:48,909 --> 00:38:51,019
the ledger which threatened your peak.

00:38:51,019 --> 00:38:53,139
E will be safe from commerce.

00:38:53,139 --> 00:39:00,380
There remains only the reform of certain habits which invite rogues as cheese invites mice.

00:39:00,380 --> 00:39:01,799
..

00:39:01,799 --> 00:39:08,940
Oh, sir, I am ashamed to the bone, and yet I confess I should not have learned caution had I not been endangered.

00:39:08,940 --> 00:39:15,320
If gratitude can mess shame, then I am free. If not, I shall bear it quietly.

00:39:15,320 --> 00:39:20,320
Holmes placed upon the table the counterfeit casket and beside it the crystal charm.

00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:35,219
Now mated to its twin, which he had found among the Colonel's effects, the two together made a tiny parody of a pair of children's shoes, and I could not but reflect upon the childishness of grown persons when romance offers to escort them to ruin in a carriage drawn by adjectives.

00:39:35,219 --> 00:39:40,920
The charm bears a needle mark, your grace, which ties it indelibly to the ledger.

00:39:40,920 --> 00:39:45,139
The same hand that thought to sign his trinkets signed his downfall.

00:39:45,139 --> 00:39:51,059
Let it remind the household that nothing is so dangerous as an original scoundrel.

00:39:51,059 --> 00:39:57,680
For originality flatters our vanity and so loosens the strings of our purse.

00:39:57,680 --> 00:40:03,820
You have my thanks, Anne, if you will not be insulted by the word, my affection.

00:40:03,820 --> 00:40:07,980
And yet there is one debt I would pay more immediately.

00:40:07,980 --> 00:40:13,860
A debt to this young woman who has been accused in my hearing of a carelessness she never practiced.

00:40:13,860 --> 00:40:16,720
...

00:40:16,720 --> 00:40:20,690
Your Grace, I am sorry. I meant no harm.

00:40:20,690 --> 00:40:25,369
I lend my ribbon to a lady who spoke kindly and I dreamed of the gallery.

00:40:25,369 --> 00:40:28,880
I shall speak less and dream harder if you forgive me.

00:40:28,880 --> 00:40:30,519
Forgive her, Your Grace.

00:40:30,519 --> 00:40:35,000
She has learned truth faster than she would have learned fear.

00:40:35,000 --> 00:40:36,219
..

00:40:36,219 --> 00:40:39,900
And that is the proper education of a servant as of a prince.

00:40:39,900 --> 00:40:43,109
Miss Hart's curiosity was of the useful sort.

00:40:43,109 --> 00:40:48,000
If Alice had denied her ribbon, we should still be searching the wrong pockets.

00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:51,059
Then I forgive and will say no more.

00:40:51,059 --> 00:40:53,369
Yet, Mr. Hunt, no.

00:40:53,369 --> 00:40:57,860
Combs, I must ask, what led you to the Colonel first,

00:40:57,860 --> 00:41:02,989
when there were any number of dandies who might have worn a silver mask and quoted a silly line.

00:41:02,989 --> 00:41:09,529
His gate, your grace, a military exactness softened by indulgence,

00:41:09,529 --> 00:41:16,890
the fox's head cane engraved in Bombay, thrown away as decoration by those who have never been,

00:41:16,890 --> 00:41:22,699
the clean-shaven cheek where an Indian climate makes shaving a purgatory for the unpractised,

00:41:22,699 --> 00:41:30,789
and, most tellingly, a watcher's eyes that measured exits as a quartermaster measures crates.

00:41:30,789 --> 00:41:37,409
He was the only guest at the river who looked for a staircase before he looked for a star.

00:41:37,409 --> 00:41:39,329
The Duchess nodded.

00:41:39,329 --> 00:41:41,159
No, Huml, call it a sing.

00:41:41,159 --> 00:41:45,019
As people nod when they recognize wisdom they cannot administer yet,

00:41:45,019 --> 00:41:49,289
would gladly employ, and she excused herself to speak with Beatrice in private,

00:41:49,289 --> 00:41:52,539
Holmes and I took our leave, and in the cab he turned to me with

00:41:52,539 --> 00:41:58,159
that look which promises a lesson. If only I keep my vanity out of the way and my ears open.

00:41:58,159 --> 00:42:05,760
Watson, what did you observe about Miss Hart's entrance at the embankment that I did not mention

00:42:05,760 --> 00:42:13,039
but nevertheless relied upon when I elected to trust her? She spoke as if she had foreknowledge

00:42:13,039 --> 00:42:18,739
of our positions, dire, and yet she did not signal to the watchers who fled. Perhaps her courage was

00:42:18,739 --> 00:42:24,079
too sincere for a conspirator's habits. Also, her shoes were wet at the toe, as if she had crossed

00:42:24,079 --> 00:42:29,300
from a skiff and yet she came from the top. That suggested she had done more than approach. She had

00:42:29,300 --> 00:42:31,820
already reconnoitered the stare and found it spoiled.

00:42:31,820 --> 00:42:33,000
..

00:42:33,000 --> 00:42:34,440
Um, excellent, hmm.

00:42:34,440 --> 00:42:36,440
..

00:42:36,440 --> 00:42:42,019
My dear fellow, the wet toes spoke more loudly than her eloquence. And there was the ribbon

00:42:42,019 --> 00:42:47,639
clasp with soap we found earlier. They seldom sell those to men who blackmail ladies.

00:42:47,639 --> 00:42:51,890
all pointed to a woman of inquiry rather than of intrigue.

00:42:51,890 --> 00:42:52,630
Ah!

00:42:52,630 --> 00:42:55,690
We'll return to Baker Street where the kettle sang and the violin waited.

00:42:55,690 --> 00:42:57,210
He took it up and played so.

00:42:57,210 --> 00:42:57,750
Hmm.

00:42:57,750 --> 00:42:58,409
Heftly.

00:42:58,409 --> 00:42:58,739
Hmm.

00:42:58,739 --> 00:43:02,019
A series of notes that rose like childhood recollections

00:43:02,019 --> 00:43:03,719
and then fell at peace.

00:43:03,719 --> 00:43:05,880
He paused and smiled in that rare human way

00:43:05,880 --> 00:43:07,789
that makes him, for an instant,

00:43:07,789 --> 00:43:09,320
less a machine of logic

00:43:09,320 --> 00:43:11,970
and more the man who cherishes his friend.

00:43:11,970 --> 00:43:14,579
Do not despise these little dramas.

00:43:14,579 --> 00:43:15,320
Watson,

00:43:15,320 --> 00:43:19,320
They are the steam that drives the engine of human motive.

00:43:19,320 --> 00:43:27,489
But I confess I prefer the clean click of a fact seated properly in its notch to the size of a duchess.

00:43:27,489 --> 00:43:34,409
The morning will bring newspapers, and we must prevent them from making a pantomime of our police.

00:43:34,409 --> 00:43:40,539
Speaking of newspapers, gentlemen, may a reporter trespass upon domestic felicity to return a ribbon

00:43:40,539 --> 00:43:44,179
to a conscientious maid and a debt of thanks to two men

00:43:44,179 --> 00:43:47,369
who keep London's masks from eating its faces?

00:43:47,369 --> 00:43:50,980
She stood at our door with the boldness peculiar to honest women

00:43:50,980 --> 00:43:52,880
who have chosen an immodest profess.

00:43:52,880 --> 00:43:56,720
Yawn. Holmes bade her enter with the courtesy he never denies to merit.

00:43:56,720 --> 00:44:00,430
She laid the ribbon upon our table as a soldier lays down a medal,

00:44:00,430 --> 00:44:02,260
lightly and with pride.

00:44:02,260 --> 00:44:04,230
I have written my piece.

00:44:04,230 --> 00:44:05,639
It names no lady.

00:44:05,639 --> 00:44:07,199
It praises no villain.

00:44:07,199 --> 00:44:09,860
And it credits the police with all the craft

00:44:09,860 --> 00:44:15,449
and Mr. Holmes with all the art, if you object to the balance, I will rebalance to your taste,

00:44:15,449 --> 00:44:21,920
but I would rather keep my integrity than my post. Keep both. The truth is often more saleable than

00:44:21,920 --> 00:44:29,739
the lie. When one can afford it, tell me, Miss Hart, who, why you took such risk as to dance

00:44:29,739 --> 00:44:35,360
on the very edge of the Colonel's watchfulness, without the comfort of a warrant to hold you

00:44:35,360 --> 00:44:41,539
if you slipped. Because I am tired of reading tragedies in which the innocent are scolded

00:44:41,539 --> 00:44:51,510
and the clever are admired. For their cleverness I wished once to admire sense and scold wickedness,

00:44:51,510 --> 00:44:57,559
and if I may say so without impropriety, because I saw a Lady Beatrice, a girl whose foolishness

00:44:57,559 --> 00:45:03,400
resembled mine at seventeen, and I thought I could pay back a debt to a world that had been

00:45:03,400 --> 00:45:08,800
been unreasonably patient with me. Holmes listened gravely and then, in a gesture rare for him,

00:45:08,800 --> 00:45:13,159
bowed as if to an equal on a field where the rules were unwritten. I felt in that moment a

00:45:13,159 --> 00:45:17,599
stirring of my own admiration that had less to do with the drama of the case and more to do with

00:45:17,599 --> 00:45:21,840
the quiet heroism that occasionally flowers in the soil of London's ordinary streets.

00:45:21,840 --> 00:45:28,739
If you keep to that creed, you will be unpopular in certain circles and immortal in a few. Do not

00:45:28,739 --> 00:45:35,730
permit editors to subtract your courage with their blue pencils and fard.

00:45:35,730 --> 00:45:42,300
Watson, do remember that a deduction is only a kindness

00:45:42,300 --> 00:45:47,160
when it saves someone pain more than it causes embarrassment.

00:45:47,160 --> 00:45:50,470
He turned again to his violin and duos.

00:45:50,470 --> 00:45:53,960
Violin and, for a while in the room, held nothing but music

00:45:53,960 --> 00:45:55,579
and the faint crackle of the goal.

00:45:55,579 --> 00:46:02,309
outside, at, the city side and bent on being itself, surly, magnificent, credulous, cunning,

00:46:02,309 --> 00:46:06,519
until a rap at the downstairs door reminded us that reputation is a vigilant creditor

00:46:06,519 --> 00:46:09,659
and often demands payment when the peace is barely over.

00:46:09,659 --> 00:46:12,520
Hmm, Mr. Hmm, Holmes.

00:46:12,520 --> 00:46:14,059
Dop the tidings.

00:46:14,059 --> 00:46:19,430
Sir Alistair has attempted magnanimity, offering to name names if we would permit him discretion.

00:46:19,430 --> 00:46:22,739
He underestimates the appetite of justice for such banquets.

00:46:22,739 --> 00:46:29,599
I thought you would like to know that our man intends to turn fairy godmother in his cell and conjure a pumpkin carriage for himself.

00:46:29,599 --> 00:46:30,960
..

00:46:30,960 --> 00:46:32,670
Decline his invitation.

00:46:32,670 --> 00:46:40,109
Lestrade, he will give you all without bargaining when he sees that his glitter has ceased to dazzle.

00:46:40,109 --> 00:46:48,650
Assure him that the one mercy the law extends to men like him is the mercy of procedure which is indifferent to charm.

00:46:48,650 --> 00:46:51,639
As succinct as a warrant, Mr. Dodd.

00:46:51,639 --> 00:46:55,340
Holmes, I shall leave you to your music and your morals

00:46:55,340 --> 00:46:57,960
Good night, doctor, and nurse your shoulder

00:46:57,960 --> 00:47:02,059
A cavalry cane leaves a bruise that enjoys its own company

00:47:02,059 --> 00:47:04,579
Lestrade departed, Miss Hart at his side

00:47:04,579 --> 00:47:07,239
To secure the dull particulars that make lively copy

00:47:07,239 --> 00:47:09,960
Holmes set down the bow and turned once more to me

00:47:09,960 --> 00:47:12,599
With that half-smile, which is his reward to my endurance

00:47:12,599 --> 00:47:14,199
And perhaps my only fee

00:47:14,199 --> 00:47:17,460
You executed your part well, Watson

00:47:17,460 --> 00:47:20,519
You closed with the colonel precisely at the syllable

00:47:20,519 --> 00:47:26,599
when rhetoric would have been fatal, I could not have done better myself. Though I might have done

00:47:26,599 --> 00:47:33,219
it earlier, which would have spoiled our evidence, and now, if you insist upon learning, you shall

00:47:33,219 --> 00:47:39,340
tell me what the two underlines in the note signified, besides the stair position.

00:47:39,340 --> 00:47:44,360
They signified, I believe, the presence of two watchers rather than one, and the necessity to

00:47:44,360 --> 00:47:50,219
occupy both with some rival spectacle, which Miss Hart provided simply by existing where she

00:47:50,219 --> 00:47:51,740
she ought not to have been.

00:47:51,740 --> 00:47:53,690
Admirable my dear fellow,

00:47:53,690 --> 00:47:54,710
you grow.

00:47:54,710 --> 00:47:57,159
Soon I shall be unemployed,

00:47:57,159 --> 00:47:58,430
or worse,

00:47:58,430 --> 00:48:01,119
celebrated beyond usefulness.

00:48:01,119 --> 00:48:02,430
To bed now,

00:48:02,430 --> 00:48:03,679
and in the morning

00:48:03,679 --> 00:48:05,329
you may write your chronicle,

00:48:05,329 --> 00:48:07,019
which I shall not read,

00:48:07,019 --> 00:48:09,420
and yet somehow always respect.

00:48:09,420 --> 00:48:10,659
The days which followed

00:48:10,659 --> 00:48:12,059
had that curious quiet

00:48:12,059 --> 00:48:13,360
which overruns London

00:48:13,360 --> 00:48:15,099
after a public scandal has been.

00:48:15,099 --> 00:48:16,159
Neatly avoided,

00:48:16,159 --> 00:48:17,779
there is a silence made.

00:48:17,779 --> 00:48:18,940
I think,

00:48:18,940 --> 00:48:32,619
By the absence of gossip that might have been, the Duchess sent a carriage of orchids with a note as restrained as an epitaph and Lady Beardress wrote to Miss Hart asking for a copy of the article in which no one was named and everyone was saved.

00:48:32,619 --> 00:48:33,740
..

00:48:33,740 --> 00:48:39,599
Observe, Watson, how the world is content to forget the very tragedies it thirsted to hear,

00:48:39,599 --> 00:48:43,590
provided it may applaud its own discretion afterward.

00:48:43,590 --> 00:48:48,519
The public is a narrator who leaves out the inconvenient chapters

00:48:48,519 --> 00:48:51,000
and credits itself with the moral,

00:48:51,000 --> 00:48:55,400
we, fortunately, are bound to a stricter memory.

00:48:55,400 --> 00:48:56,599
..

00:48:56,599 --> 00:48:58,930
Sir Alistair, as Lestrade later informed us,

00:48:58,930 --> 00:49:02,139
confessed with a prolixity that would have done credit to a novelist

00:49:02,139 --> 00:49:07,760
paid by the line, the gunner remained staunch and sour, and sour, but his pockets gave up a great

00:49:07,760 --> 00:49:12,750
many small instruments, which, connected together, made a school of deception so well equipped,

00:49:12,750 --> 00:49:18,400
that I marvelled we had caught it with so little injury. Your man sang, Mr. Holmes, in the bass of

00:49:18,400 --> 00:49:23,360
a gentleman and the treble of a coward. He gave us names, accounts, and a list of future fetts he

00:49:23,360 --> 00:49:28,579
meant to harvest. For once I shall go to a ball to cancel it, and I will dance with every hostess

00:49:28,579 --> 00:49:31,099
to prove the police can turn better than a rogue.

00:49:31,099 --> 00:49:32,139
..

00:49:32,139 --> 00:49:34,369
Hey, dance with care.

00:49:34,369 --> 00:49:37,569
Lestrade, the law's toes are tender.

00:49:37,569 --> 00:49:40,219
And remember to send the Duchess her jewels

00:49:40,219 --> 00:49:43,420
after they have been stared at the proper length

00:49:43,420 --> 00:49:45,680
by the proper authorities.

00:49:45,680 --> 00:49:46,510
Eee!

